# vhs tape — English demo GIF. Render: vhs docs/assets/demo-en.tape
Output docs/assets/demo-en.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 960
Set Height 640
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 45ms
Set Padding 16

Hide
Type `export PATH="/tmp/geo-bin:$PATH" LANG=en_US.UTF-8 && clear`
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "geo-doctor audit stripe.com --html"
Sleep 800ms
Enter
Sleep 16s
Sleep 4s
